  <center><img src=/update/21003/rzdead.jpg></center><br><br>

<center>Yes, the curse DOES continue for FE; you see, whenever a mob 
drops a certainly highly sought after weapon or piece of gear, it simply 
does not drop it UNTIL our competition gets to the mob...  Tonight we 
killed RZ for the 3rd time in hopes of equipping our instagibbing non 
aggro holding warriors with a Blade of War or two... No such luck my 
friends, no such luck.  I would imagine that RZ will indeed start to 
drop 
a BoW now and again for the competition in a few months. It's simply the 
bane of FE and the monkey on our backs that we simply can't shake.    
The 
event has changed and it's a good change, the entire event, save for 
part 
of the finish is really rather well planned and scripted.  It's not too 
long, not to short, has just enough white knuckling the mouse and drops 
some fairly worth while loots... </center><br>

<center><img src=/update/21003/loot01.jpg></center><br><center>Grats 
Nadime</center><br>
<center><img src=/update/21003/loot02.jpg></center><br><center>Grats 
Cydmab</center><br><br><center>Off to PoAir we go... The Big Breasted 
Sister of Aten Ha Ra awaits!!!</center>

